source.name: Number of Producible and Service Completions on Federal Lands
source.description: This table contains the total number of producible and service completions, by state, during each fiscal year.  Separate service completions are for the benefit of oil and gas operations, such as water disposal, salt water disposal, water injection, gas injection, water source, steam injection, or monitoring.
